query:
UPDATE users
               SET email = $2, role = $3, updated_at = datetime('now', 'subsec')
               WHERE id = $1
               RETURNING id as "id!: Uuid",
                         username,
                         email,
                         password_hash,
                         role,
                         created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                         updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
